title: Keith Spence and Brian North visit the Free Press Football Show to talk about Greene Central-Kinston showdown
text: Keith Spence and Brian North visit the Free Press Football Show to talk about Greene Central-Kinston showdown By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III The Free Press By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 8:11 PM Updated at 9:31 PM By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 8:11 PM Updated at 9:31 PM Longtime Free Press sports correspondent Keith Spence and WCTI ABC-12/Fox Eastern Carolina's Brian North join Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III to talk about the Greene Central-Kinston football showdown on this week's Free Press Football Show. Bryan and Junious also take a look at all of last week's games and preview the other big games in this week's show. CLICK HERE to stream or download the show. By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III The Free Press By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 8:11 PM Updated at 9:31 PM
